First Report of Alternaria japonica, a causal agent of black spot, on kale in 
South Carolina, United States.

Keinath AP(1), Toporek SM(2), DuBose V(3), Zardus SH(4), Ballew JB(5).

Author information:
(1)Clemson University, Coastal REC, 2700 Savannah Hwy, Charleston, South 
Carolina, United States, 29414-5329; tknth@clemson.edu.
(2)Clemson University College of Agriculture Forestry and Life Sciences, 114625, 
Plant and Environmental Sciences, 2700 Savannah Hwy, Charleston, Charleston, 
